 interests ranging from Engineering and Construction, Cement, Private Hydropower, Hospitality, Information Technology, and Real- estate- Development- to Expressways-and-Highways. Jaiprakash Associates Limited the flagship of the Jaypee Group As a Resident Engineer (Electrical) and Shift in charge of a prestigious Tunnel project, associated with the assembly, testing, commissioning, and operation of a Hard Rock Double Shield Tunnel Boring Machine. Presently executing the project of boring a 10 m diameter, 45 Km underground tunnel in association with M/s Robbins Tunneling and Trenchless Technology Ltd, USA. Yashraj Biotechnology Ltd. It is innovating in the diagnostics space to make a healthier world. From being a Native Antigen manufacturer, they substantially enhanced their portfolio over the years to become a premium provider of IVD raw materials and pre-clinical drug discovery services. Our relentless passion to make a healthier world drives us to continually focus on the emerging unmet needs in the diagnostics space and become the preferred partner to our customers As a Collection Associate my responsibility is to make agreements with hospitals for the collection of AF / PF body fluids from cancer patients urine of Renel failure patients and HBSAG +ve (reactive) plasma from hepatitis patients for research. RESPONSIBILITY Forecasting / Planning and execution of day-to-day technical requirements. Optimum utilization of workforce as well as plant & machinery by their judicious deployment cater for the requirement of day-to-day operations. Forecasting the requirement and ensuring their timely availability of support services like Pipelines, H.T cables, etc. Erection of poles for overhead lines and cabling, grounding, and earthing of panels. Execution of Electrical work according to the approved design & drawings. Scheduling periodic maintenance, preventive maintenance and to reduce breakdowns maintenance. Ensuring availability of adequate lighting and ventilation inside the tunnel and on the machine. Responsible for the safety of the workforce deployed on the shift both on and outside the machine. Experience in the Erection, Commissioning, and Dismantling of the Robbins Gripper Double Shield Tunnel boring machine. Operation, maintenance, and troubleshooting of Robbins Gripper Double Shield Tunnel boring machine. Erection of Electrical panels and equipment based on requirement. Maintenance of Electrical sub-station of 33/11kv and switch yard (1*1.5MVA 1*6.3 MVA) capacity. Different types of H.T. cable jointing for both 24 & 11kv lines. Erection, Commissioning & Testing of 910X6 KVA DG sets and their GCP& PLC-based auto synchronizing panels. Erection, Commissioning & Testing of 33/22/11Kv VCB, CT, PT, GOS & 6300Kva power transformers in substation. All works related to HT cabling33/22/11KV (like Heat & Cold Shrinkable End & Straight Jointing). Forecasting / Planning and execution of day-to-day technical requirements. Have to visit Super specialty / Multispecialty hospitals to make an appointment with the Director or Manager / MS of the Hospitals. Have to explain the project and then after we go through an Agreement/ M.O.U. with hospitals. Have to meet with the H.O.D. of the concerned Departments (Oncology, Diabetology, Gastroenterology, Nephrology) about this project and sometimes have to show the government approvals for handling transporting and proper treatment of remaining residual biomedical waste. After agreement need to train the medical staff about handling and collecting biomedical fluid of the concerned department."}]'::jsonb, '[{"title":"Imported project details","description":"Preparing and monitoring resource requirements based on the budgetary parameters, make || changes in the same as per revised schedules and budgets || Tracking and control cost accruals based with respect to budgets. || Generating progress reports, monitor project status, cost and time reconciliation. || Managing overall operations for executing 